sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant TM as TrafficMonitor Main Program
    participant PM as PowerMon Plugin (ITMPlugin)
    participant CM as ConfigManager
    participant BR as BatteryReader
    participant PR as PdhPowerReader
    participant GR as GpuPowerReader
    participant PI as PowerMonItem (IPluginItem)

    Note over TM, PI: 轮询周期触发：每秒调用一次 DataRequired()

    TM->>PM: DataRequired()
    PM->>CM: GetSetting()
    CM-->>PM: return SettingData (cached)
    PM->>PM: GetSystemPowerStatus()

    alt 供电状态为电池模式 (DC Mode)
        PM->>BR: GetBatteryDischargeRate(out_power)
        alt 电池读取成功
            BR-->>PM: return true (out_power = DischargeRate)
        else 电池读取失败 (回退/未装电池)
            BR-->>PM: return false
            PM->>PM: 设为 0.0 W
        end
        
        alt 智能显示模式启用 (smart_mode == true)
            PM->>PI: UpdateValue(电池放电功率, setting)
            Note over PM, PI: 只显示并更新【电池监控子项】，其他子项设为 0.0 W 或不渲染
        else 智能模式未启用
            PM->>PI: UpdateValue(各对应子项数据, setting)
        end

    else 供电状态为电源模式 (AC Mode)
        alt 开启 CPU 监控 (cpu_mon_enable == true)
            PM->>PR: GetCpuPower(out_power)
            alt PDH 读取成功
                PR-->>PM: return true (out_power = CPU Power)
            else PDH 失败，回退 WMI
                PR->>PR: GetCpuPowerFallbackWmi(out_power)
                alt WMI 成功
                    PR-->>PM: return true
                else WMI 失败，使用静态估算
                    PR->>PR: GetCpuPowerStaticEstimation(out_power)
                    PR-->>PM: return true (out_power = 静态估算值)
                end
                PR-->>PM: return true
            end
        else CPU 监控关闭
            PM->>PM: CPU 功耗 = 0.0 W
        end

        alt 开启 GPU 监控 (gpu_mon_enable == true)
            PM->>GR: GetGpuPower(out_power)
            alt 处于低功耗防频繁唤醒控制 (Timer check)
                GR-->>PM: return true (out_power = 上次缓存值/0.0W)
            else 执行真正的硬件轮询
                alt NVML 动态加载并可用 (NVIDIA)
                    GR-->>PM: return true (out_power = GPU Power)
                else ADL 动态加载并可用 (AMD)
                    GR-->>PM: return true (out_power = GPU Power)
                else 回退 D3DKMT 通用查询
                    GR->>GR: GetD3dKmtPower(out_power)
                    GR-->>PM: return true
                end
            end
        else GPU 监控关闭
            PM->>PM: GPU 功耗 = 0.0 W
        end

        alt 智能显示模式启用 (smart_mode == true)
            PM->>PI: UpdateValue(CPU功耗 + GPU功耗, setting)
            Note over PM, PI: 只显示并更新【智能合并监控子项】，其他设为 0.0 W 或不渲染
        else 智能模式未启用
            PM->>PI: UpdateValue(各对应子项数据, setting)
        end
    end

    TM->>PI: GetItemValueText()
    PI-->>TM: return Formatted String (遵循 digit_length, spacing_control, unit_string)
    TM->>TM: 渲染至状态栏或悬浮窗
